condition.narrative: Schedule 2. Section I. A3The Recipient, not later than three months after the Effective Date shall create and thereafter maintain,at all times until the completion of the Project, a unit in each Conservation Area Landscape, each led by a unit coordinator andincluding safeguards and value chain specialists, with a mandate and resources satisfactory to the Association. These units willcoordinate Project implementation activities in their respective Conservation Area Landscapes.
